info.author: Dave Hall
info.description:
jutsu
=====

**jutsu** is a HTTP library for asyncio.


Features
--------

- WSGI web server.


Installation
------------

1. Install using ``pip install jutsu``.


Build status
------------

This project is built on every push using the Travis-CI service.

.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/etianen/jutsu.svg?branch=master
    :target: https://travis-ci.org/etianen/jutsu


Support and announcements
-------------------------

Downloads and bug tracking can be found at the `main project
website <http://github.com/etianen/jutsu>`_.

    
More information
----------------

The jutsu project was developed by Dave Hall. You can get the code
from the `jutsu project site <http://github.com/etianen/jutsu>`_.
    
Dave Hall is a freelance web developer, based in Cambridge, UK. You can usually
find him on the Internet in a number of different places:

-  `Website <http://www.etianen.com/>`_
-  `Twitter <http://twitter.com/etianen>`_
-  `Google Profile <http://www.google.com/profiles/david.etianen>`_
